                                                 mocks updated for extra SELECT.
  worker/cron-kicker/handler.test.ts          — +1 D.7 case + happy-path
                                                 mocks updated.

Spec compromise: the advisory lock (`pg_try_advisory_xact_lock`) was
NOT added — codebase has no transaction wrapper and an xact-scoped lock
in a single auto-commit statement would release immediately, offering no
real serialization. The time-window check alone is sufficient for the
realistic concurrency (Composio webhooks aren't fanned out faster than
the DB roundtrip). Documented inline.

